        {
            "+content": "Elsa, the daughter of a fallen aristocrat, receives news. It was a marriage proposal from Julius, a very elite nobleman. Elsa wondered why such a distinguished man would propose to her. But after the wedding, Julius, who had been kind and gentle up to that point, changed completely. In a cold voice, he tells her, \"I have no intention of loving you.\" <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
